    • paintIcon

      public void paintIcon​(Component C, Graphics g, int x, int y)
      Paints this BoxIcon. Drawing and filling colors are determined by the color values set - if none, then defaults are taken from C. Default filling color for unfilled points is the background color of C.
      Specified by:
      paintIcon in interface Icon
      Parameters:
      C - a component, not null
      g - graphics context
      x - X coordinate for upper left corner of icon.
      y - Y coordinate for upper left corner of icon.
